<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="感通" xml:id="gsz0840b24shiJianKong"><lb
ed="T" n="0840b24"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0840b24"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>洛陽香山寺<persName key="A012674">鑑空</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0840b25"/><persName key="A012674">釋鑑空</persName>，俗姓齊，<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳郡</placeName>人也。少小苦貧，雖勤<lb
ed="T" n="0840b26"/>於學而寡記持。壯歲為詩，不多靡麗。常困<lb
ed="T" n="0840b27"/>遊<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000010514">楚</placeName>間，已四、五年矣。干謁侯伯，所潤無<lb
ed="T" n="0840b28"/>幾。錢或盈貫，則必病生，用罄方差。<date notBefore-iso="+0806-01-29" key="j20154742016757" notAfter-iso="+0809-08-04"><name>元和</name>初</date><lb
ed="T" n="0840b29"/>遊<placeName key="PL000000011520">錢塘</placeName>，屬其荒儉，乃議求餐於<placeName key="PLG00000000023">天竺寺</placeName>。至<pb ed="T" n="0840c" xml:id="T50.2061.0840c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0840c01"/><placeName key="PL000000011648">孤山寺</placeName>西，餒甚不前，因臨流雪涕，悲吟數<lb
ed="T" n="0840c02"/>聲。俄有<name>梵</name>僧臨流而坐，顧<persName key="A012674">空</persName>笑曰：「<persName key="A012674">法師</persName>秀<lb
ed="T" n="0840c03"/>才，旅遊滋味足未？」<persName key="A012674">空</persName>曰：「旅遊滋味則已足矣。<lb
ed="T" n="0840c04"/>法師之呼，一何乖謬？」蓋以<persName key="A012674">空</persName>未為僧時名<persName key="A012674">君<lb
ed="T" n="0840c05"/>房</persName>也。<name>梵</name>僧曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012674">子</ref>不憶講《法華經》於<placeName key="PL000000023593">同德寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0840c06"/>乎？」<persName key="A012674">空</persName>曰：「生身已四十五歲矣，盤桓<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000010514">楚</placeName>間，<lb
ed="T" n="0840c07"/>未甞涉<placeName key="PL000000010985">京口</placeName>。又何<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛中</placeName>之說？」僧曰：「<persName key="A012674">子</persName>應為<lb
ed="T" n="0840c08"/>飢火所燒，不暇憶故事。」遂探囊出一棗，<lb
ed="T" n="0840c09"/>大如拳許，曰：「此吾國所產，食之者，上智知<lb
ed="T" n="0840c10"/>過去未來事，下智止於知前生事耳。」<persName key="A012674">空</persName>飢<lb
ed="T" n="0840c11"/>極食棗，掬泉飲之。忽欠呻，枕石而寢，頃刻<lb
ed="T" n="0840c12"/>乃悟，憶講經於<placeName key="PL000000023593">同德寺</placeName>如昨日焉。因增涕<lb
ed="T" n="0840c13"/>泣，問僧曰：「<persName key="A012725">震和尚</persName>安在？」曰：「專精未至，再為<lb
ed="T" n="0840c14"/><placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>僧矣。今則斷攀<anchor xml:id="beg0840sgsz1"/>緣<anchor xml:id="end0840sgsz1"/>也。」「<persName key="A012726">神上人</persName>安在？」曰：「前<lb
ed="T" n="0840c15"/>願未滿。」「<persName key="A012727">悟法師</persName>焉在？」曰：「豈不記<placeName key="PL000000023650">香山</placeName>石像<lb
ed="T" n="0840c16"/>前戲發大願乎？若不證無上菩提，必願為<lb
ed="T" n="0840c17"/>赳赳貴臣。昨聞已得大將軍矣。當時雲水五<lb
ed="T" n="0840c18"/>人，<anchor xml:id="beg0840sgsz3"/>唯<anchor xml:id="end0840sgsz3"/>吾得解脫，獨<persName key="A012674">汝</persName>為凍餒之士也。」<persName key="A012674">空</persName>泣<lb
ed="T" n="0840c19"/>曰：「<persName key="A012674">某</persName>四十許年日唯一餐，三十餘年擁一褐，<lb
ed="T" n="0840c20"/>浮俗之事決斷根源。何期福不完乎，坐於飢<lb
ed="T" n="0840c21"/>凍！」僧曰：「由師子座上廣說異端，使學空之<lb
ed="T" n="0840c22"/>人心生疑惑。戒珠曾缺，羶氣微存，聲渾響清，<lb
ed="T" n="0840c23"/>終不可致。質傴影曲，報應宜然。」<persName key="A012674">空</persName>曰：「為之<lb
ed="T" n="0840c24"/>奈何？」僧曰：「今日之事，吾無計矣。他生之事，<lb
ed="T" n="0840c25"/>警於<ref type="person" target="#A012674">吾子</ref>焉。」乃探鉢囊取一鑑，背面皆瑩<lb
ed="T" n="0840c26"/>徹，謂<persName key="A012674">空</persName>曰：「要知貴賤之分，脩短之期，佛法<lb
ed="T" n="0840c27"/>興<anchor xml:id="beg0840sgsz5"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>賛</sic><corr>替</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0840sgsz5"/>，吾道盛衰，宜一鑒焉。」<persName key="A012674">空</persName>覽照久之，謝<lb
ed="T" n="0840c28"/>曰：「報應之事，榮枯之理，謹知之矣。」僧收鑑<lb
ed="T" n="0840c29"/>入囊，遂挈而去，行十餘步，旋失所在。<persName key="A012674">空</persName>是<pb ed="T" n="0841a" xml:id="T50.2061.0841a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0841a01"/>夕投<placeName key="PL000000011596">靈隱寺</placeName>出家，受具足戒。後周遊名山，<lb
ed="T" n="0841a02"/>愈高苦節。<date from-iso="+0827-03-18" key="j20231922023504" to-iso="+0828-01-24">大和元年</date>詣<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛陽</placeName>，於龍門<placeName key="PL000000023662">天竺<lb
ed="T" n="0841a03"/>寺</placeName>遇<placeName key="PL000000005197">河東</placeName><persName key="A012733">柳珵</persName>，親說厥由向<persName key="A012733">珵</persName>。<persName key="A012733">珵</persName>聞<persName key="A012674">空</persName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0841a04"/>說，事皆不常，且甚奇之。<persName key="A012674">空</persName>曰：「<persName key="A012674">我</persName>生世七十<lb
ed="T" n="0841a05"/>有七，僧臘三十二，持鉢乞食，尚九年在世。<persName key="A012674">吾</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0841a06"/>捨世之日，佛法其衰乎？」<persName key="A012733">珵</persName>詰之，默然無答。<lb
ed="T" n="0841a07"/>乃索<anchor xml:id="beg0841sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>䄇</sic><corr>珵</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0841sgsz1"/>筆硯，題數行於經藏北垣而去。曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0841a08"/>「興一沙衰恒河沙，兔而罝，犬而拏，牛虎相<lb
ed="T" n="0841a09"/>交與角牙，寶檀終不滅其華。」</p>
    <p xml:id="pT50p0841a1001"><lb
ed="T" n="0841a10"/>系曰：食<name>梵</name>僧之棗而知宿命者，與茹<placeName key="PL000000047443">雪山</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0841a11"/>之藥解諸國言音同也。覽鑑而知吉凶者，<lb
ed="T" n="0841a12"/>與窺<persName key="A002277">圖澄</persName>塗麻掌同也。食棗臨鑑，豈偶然<lb
ed="T" n="0841a13"/>耶？非常人之遇也。其<persName key="A012674">空公</persName>題讖而答，塞<persName key="A012733">柳<lb
ed="T" n="0841a14"/>珵</persName>之問，驗在<date from-iso="+0841-02-08" key="j20282682030170" to-iso="+0846-04-25"><name>會昌</name></date>之毀教矣。時<persName key="A006570">武宗</persName>勒僧<lb
ed="T" n="0841a15"/>尼反俗，計二十萬七千餘人，坼寺并蘭若<lb
ed="T" n="0841a16"/>共四萬七千有奇，故云「興一沙衰恒河沙，<lb
ed="T" n="0841a17"/>兔在罝，犬仍拏」，言殘害之甚。<date from-iso="+0845-02-15" key="j20297362030089" to-iso="+0846-02-03">乙丑</date>毀法，<date from-iso="+0846-02-04" key="j20300902030170" to-iso="+0846-04-25">丙寅</date><lb
ed="T" n="0841a18"/>厭代，佛法喻寶檀之樹，終不絕其華蘤芬<lb
ed="T" n="0841a19"/>馥，故云也。苟非異人，何以藏往考來之若<lb
ed="T" n="0841a20"/>是乎？</p>
